#

No-Knead Whole Wheat Bread

75 min
$2.5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 10

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianWhole Grain

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Bread

Tags:

BreadEasyHealthy

Description

This easy, no-knead whole wheat bread is crusty on the outside and soft on the inside, perfect for sandwiches or toasting.

Ingredients

  • whole wheat flour: 3 cups
  • water: 1.5 cups
  • salt: 1.5 tsp
  • instant yeast: 1 tsp
  • olive oil: 1 tbsp
